-----------
 Libraries
-----------
Required Libraries: - boost (http://www.boost.org/)
						- boost/algorithm/string/split.hpp
						- boost/lexical_cast.hpp
					- SimpleCUI (https://github.com/felixwiemuth/SimpleCUI)
					- SimpleLog (https://github.com/felixwiemuth/SimpleLog)

-------------
 Description
-------------

PokerBank is a C++ application that keeps account of the bank during a poker game.
It manages to sell chips to players and buy them back.


-------------
 Features
-------------

- management (money, number of chips, different sorts of chips, ...)
- interest on buy/sell
- logging of activity